OL,3,CPaul Mosley, jailed for manslaughter
OL,4,Cof six Philpott children, dies at 58
OL,6,FPaul Mosley, who was jailed for the
OL,7,Fmanslaughter of six children who died
OL,8,Fin a deliberate house fire in Derby,
OL,9,Fhas died at the age of 58.
OL,11,FMosley, along with the parents of the
OL,12,Fsix victims - Mick and Mairead
OL,13,FPhilpott - deliberately started a fire
OL,14,Fat the house in Allenton where the
OL,15,Fyoungsters lived, on May 11, 2012.
OL,17,FHe and the Philpotts were convicted of
OL,18,Fsix counts of manslaughter after a
OL,19,Fseven-week trial at Nottingham Crown
OL,20,FCourt.
