OL,3,CPaul Mosley, jailed for manslaughter
OL,4,Cof six Philpott children, dies at 58
OL,6,FAll were found to be responsible for
OL,7,Fthe deaths of 13-year-old Duwayne
OL,8,FPhilpott, his sister Jade, 10, and
OL,9,Fbrothers John, nine, Jack, eight,
OL,10,FJessie, six and Jayden, five.
OL,12,FMick Philpott was jailed for life
OL,13,Fwhile his wife and Mosley were each
OL,14,Fgiven 17-year sentences by Mrs Justice
OL,15,FKate Thirlwall KC.
OL,17,FMosley was released from prison in
OL,18,FNovember 2023.
