OL,3,CPaul Mosley, jailed for manslaughter
OL,4,Cof six Philpott children, dies at 58
OL,6,FMick Philpott, who was the father of
OL,7,Ffive of the children who died,
OL,8,Fenlisted his wife and friend Mosley to
OL,9,Fhelp him light the fire at the foot of
OL,10,Fthe stairs at the home in Victory Road.
OL,12,FThe plan was for him to rescue the
OL,13,Fchildren. Despite the best efforts of
OL,14,Fneighbours and the emergency services
OL,15,Fto save them, the five youngest
OL,16,Fchildren died on the day.
OL,18,FDuwayne, who was not the biological
OL,19,Fchild of Philpott, died days later
OL,20,Fwhen his life support machine was
OL,21,Fturned off.
