OL,3,CPaul Mosley, jailed for manslaughter
OL,4,Cof six Philpott children, dies at 58
OL,6,F"It was a wicked and dangerous plan"
OL,8,FAt the trial sentencing in 2013,
OL,9,FJustice Mrs Kate Thirlwell KC said:
OL,10,F"All three of you are responsible for
OL,11,Fthe deliberate setting of that fire.
OL,12,FAll three of you are responsible for
OL,13,Fthose deaths.
OL,15,F"I have not the slightest doubt that
OL,16,Fyou, Michael Philpott, were the
OL,17,Fdriving force behind this shockingly
OL,18,Fdangerous enterprise. You Mairead
OL,19,FPhilpott, the mother of all of those
OL,20,Fchildren and you, Paul Mosley, a
OL,21,Ffamily friend assisted him.
