OL,3,CPaul Mosley, jailed for manslaughter
OL,4,Cof six Philpott children, dies at 58
OL,6,F"It was a wicked and dangerous plan
OL,7,Fand you (Philpott) put it into effect
OL,8,Fwith the assistance of your two
OL,9,Fcodefendants.
OL,11,F"You poured petrol on the floor. Paul
OL,12,FMosley was responsible for removing
OL,13,Fthe containers from your home.
OL,15,FYou (Philpott) set light to it and
OL,16,Fafter a short while Mairead Philpott
OL,17,Fspoke to the emergency services, it
OL,18,Fbecame clear that there was no chance
OL,19,Fof a successful rescue and the
OL,20,Fchildren perished.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
