OL,3,CPaul Mosley, jailed for manslaughter
OL,4,Cof six Philpott children, dies at 58
OL,6,F"You (Mosley) have young children of
OL,7,Fyour own.
OL,9,F"You must have appreciated the
OL,10,Fappalling risk to which these six
OL,11,Fchildren were to be exposed when this
OL,12,Ffire was started in their home.
OL,14,F"And yet you were prepared to go along
OL,15,Fwith the plan and to join in with it
OL,16,Fto please your then friend, Michael
OL,17,FPhilpott.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOU
