OL,6,F"I am quite sure that one of your
OL,7,Ftasks that night was to remove the
OL,8,Fpetrol containers from the scene so
OL,9,Fthat the attack would appear to have
OL,10,Fcome from outside.
OL,12,F"You enjoyed the attention that you
OL,13,Fgained from your proximity to the fire.
OL,15,F"You boasted of being arrested and
OL,16,Fbailed for 6 counts of murder. You
OL,17,Fcould not help telling people that
OL,18,Fthis was a plan that had gone wrong."
